videos.headline: Sun Devils RB Benjamin bullies his way into end zone
videos.description: Eno Benjamin powers through multiple Cal defenders on his way into the end zone for an 11-yard Arizona State touchdown.

videos.headline: Sun Devils take lead with TD run

videos.headline: Benjamin runs for 3 TDs in Arizona State's upset over Cal
videos.description: Eno Benjamin tears up the Cal defense for three rushing touchdowns as Arizona State hands No. 15 Cal its first loss of the season.
